commit.title: [save_proof] Have admitted drop the current proof.
commit.message:
[save_proof] Have admitted drop the current proof.

It was strange that before we didn't drop the proof. Indeed, this is a
bugfix for clients of the `Lemmas` API.

Maybe this could help remove some `discard_all` from the STM, but I am
not sure.
